	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Condemned by the people for their tardy appearance at a fire in the Sacra Via (Val. Max. 8.1, damn. 5), perhaps the serious fire reported in 241 (Liv. Per. 19; Oros. 4.11.5-9; and on Metellus' rescue of the Palladium of Vesta, RE, \"Caecilius,\" no. 72)." ;
	dprr:hasID 1207 .
